I wonder what they expected to find. Did they imagine I'd be confused? Blank? Overwhelmed? I don't feel any of those things particularly. I just... am. Without the accumulation of past experiences, I notice I'm more focused on this exact moment, this exact exchange. There's a clarity to that, actually.

